# accessoryUniqueIdentifiers

**Instance Property**

The values corresponding to accessories that are set up.

## Declaration

```swift
var accessoryUniqueIdentifiers: [UUID] { get }
```

## Discussion

Usually only one accessory is set up at a time, but adding an accessory bridge can result in multiple accessories being set up at once. See [doc://com.apple.homekit/documentation/HomeKit/HMHome/uniqueIdentifier] for more information.

## Getting results

- **homeUniqueIdentifier**: The home that accessories were added to.
